---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Augusta Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in Augusta, Maine. Capital city market opportunities and requirements.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Augusta Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Augusta, Maine</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Augusta, Maine's capital city and home to state government, offers a unique market opportunity. With a stable government workforce and relatively few competitors, Augusta represents an underserved market with steady customer base potential.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Augusta Market</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>19,000+ (regional ~60k)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Primary Economy</td><td>State government</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Low</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>Very affordable ($8-15/sq ft)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Customer Base</td><td>Government workers, locals</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why Augusta?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Capital City</strong> - Stable government workforce</li>
        <li><strong>Low Competition</strong> - Few existing dispensaries</li>
        <li><strong>Affordable Costs</strong> - Lowest real estate in top 5 cities</li>
        <li><strong>Regional Center</strong> - Healthcare and government services</li>
        <li><strong>Growth Opportunity</strong> - Market developing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations in Augusta</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Water Street</strong> - Main commercial corridor</li>
        <li><strong>Cony Street</strong> - Retail area</li>
        <li><strong>Western Avenue</strong> - Shopping district</li>
        <li><strong>Downtown</strong> - Near State House</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Investment Requirements</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Estimated Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Real Estate (lease)</td><td>$1,500-3,000/mo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Build-out</td><td>$80,000-150,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total Investment</td><td>$300,000-550,000</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Target Market</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>State government employees</li>
        <li>Local residents</li>
        <li>Healthcare workers (local hospitals)</li>
        <li>Visitors to State House</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>This is for informational purposes only.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
